Star Watch is our handy guide to which stars are currently performing on the London stage.

West End theatre is famous for its stars: actors and actresses who are acclaimed for their work on stage, in films and on TV. Part of the glamour of London’s theatre scene is getting to see a performer at the very top of their career, doing their best work, live and in person.

London theatres are packed full of West End stars on stage, performing in drama, comedy and musicals, including Sirs and Dames of British theatre, Hollywood stars making their West End debuts in London, and young and up-and-coming talent who are forging their reputations on the London Stage.

Every night of the year, the West End offers a place to see the most famous, most talented stars, live on stage.
